{"type":"result","subtype":"success","is_error":false,"duration_ms":163977,"duration_api_ms":144094,"num_turns":19,"result":"```json\n{\n  \"change_summary\": \"Applied all four pending amendments from the final review: (1) replaced `v as u32` with `u32::try_from(v).ok()` in extract_codex_usage_from_stdout for safe overflow handling; (2) replaced `Some(p + c)` with `p.checked_add(c)` in both Claude and Codex total_tokens computations to prevent panic/wrap on overflow; (3) hardened extract_codex_usage_from_stdout to skip null, non-object, and empty usage values via `.filter(|u| u.is_object())` and an `is_none()` guard, with a regression test for `{\\\"usage\\\":null}` and `{\\\"usage\\\":{}}` trailing events; (4) moved the tracing::info! event in service.rs to fire immediately after metadata finalization, before persist_raw_output/extract_structured_payload/contract validation, so token/cache data is always traced even for malformed or contract-invalid responses.\",\n  \"steps\": [\n    {\n      \"description\": \"Replaced `.as_u64().map(|v| v as u32)` with `.as_u64().and_then(|v| u32::try_from(v).ok())` for all three token field extractions in extract_codex_usage_from_stdout (process_backend.rs:1299-1310)\",\n      \"order\": 1,\n      \"status\": \"completed\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"description\": \"Replaced `Some(p + c)` with `p.checked_add(c)` in Claude usage total_tokens computation (process_backend.rs:186)\",\n      \"order\": 2,\n      \"status\": \"completed\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"description\": \"Replaced `Some(i + o)` with `i.checked_add(o)` in Codex usage total_tokens computation (process_backend.rs:1312)\",\n      \"order\": 3,\n      \"status\": \"completed\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"description\": \"Added `.filter(|u| u.is_object())` guard to usage value extraction and `if input.is_none() && output.is_none() && cached.is_none() { continue; }` to skip usage objects with no recognized token fields (process_backend.rs:1296,1314-1316)\",\n      \"order\": 4,\n      \"status\": \"completed\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"description\": \"Added regression test codex_usage_skips_null_and_empty_usage_objects that verifies trailing `{\\\"usage\\\":null}` and `{\\\"usage\\\":{}}` events do not shadow a valid earlier usage record\",\n      \"order\": 5,\n      \"status\": \"completed\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"description\": \"Moved tracing::info! event in service.rs from after contract validation (line 262) to immediately after metadata finalization (line 239), before persist_raw_output, extract_structured_payload, and contract evaluation\",\n      \"order\": 6,\n      \"status\": \"completed\"\n    }\n  ],\n  \"validation_evidence\": [\n    \"cargo test: 330 lib + 128 cli + 1 tmux + 667 unit = 1126 tests passed, 0 failed (330 lib is up from 329 due to the new regression test)\",\n    \"cargo clippy -- -D warnings: clean, no warnings\",\n    \"cargo fmt --check: clean, no formatting issues\",\n    \"New test codex_usage_skips_null_and_empty_usage_objects passes: verifies trailing {\\\"usage\\\":null} and {\\\"usage\\\":{}} are skipped and valid earlier record (500/120/620/300) is returned\",\n    \"Existing test codex_usage_extracts_from_ndjson_stdout still passes with u32::try_from and checked_add changes\",\n    \"Existing test codex_usage_picks_last_event_with_usage still passes confirming reverse scan logic preserved\",\n    \"Existing test claude_envelope_with_usage_parses_token_counts still passes with checked_add change\"\n  ],\n  \"outstanding_risks\": []\n}\n```","stop_reason":"end_turn","session_id":"8271ac28-e625-47c7-acf1-433129ad04f7","total_cost_usd":1.4242352499999997,"usage":{"input_tokens":17,"cache_creation_input_tokens":86183,"cache_read_input_tokens":1404013,"output_tokens":7340,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":86183,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0},"inference_geo":"","iterations":[],"speed":"standard"},"m